Android service that hides and restores the android systembar.

This works on all Honeycomb, Ice Cream Sandwich and Jelly Bean devices. The
device must be rooted.

A webpage with more documentation is available at
http://ppareit.github.com/HideBar/.
The program is also available at the android market, see
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=be.ppareit.hidebar .

For comments, corrections and suggestions, contact me at
pieter.pareit@gmail.com

